- poly_derivative function: Evaluates the derivative of the polynomial at a given point x.
- find_zero function: Implements the Newton-Raphson method to find a root of the polynomial. It starts with an initial guess (x0 = 0), iterates until the function value is close to zero (within a tolerance), or reaches a maximum number of iterations.

