  - For even n, computes 1 + n / 2.
  - For odd n, recursively computes tri(n - 1) + tri(n - 2) + tri(n + 1).
- Stores the computed value in the HashMap and returns it.

This approach ensures that we efficiently compute the Tribonacci sequence using memoization to avoid redundant calculations.

